<span id="freeTextContainer14201993029835688493">Two fable-like tales of a character called Green, whose touch came make anything grow. Her village and the neighboring city experiences great loss due to a fire. The first part is her plunge into grief, taking on a new personna called Ash. She survives by helping others, animals, to heal and survive. The second part her journey back to wholeness and a new version of herself as Green is accomplished through documenting others life stories. </span>

          </span>
